### 1. Backend — Subscription Model & Schema Enhancement

Memperkuat [Tenant.js](file:///d:/DevAppTim/Warkop%20React%20-%20%20SuperKafe%20Multitenant/backend/models/Tenant.js) dengan field subscription yang lebih lengkap, dan membersihkan legacy fields.

#### [MODIFY] [Tenant.js](file:///d:/DevAppTim/Warkop%20React%20-%20%20SuperKafe%20Multitenant/backend/models/Tenant.js)

Tambahkan field baru ke Tenant schema:

```diff
 // Trial & Subscription Fields
 status: {
   type: String,
-  enum: ['trial', 'paid', 'expired', 'suspended'],
+  enum: ['trial', 'active', 'grace', 'expired', 'suspended'],
   default: 'trial'
 },
+subscriptionPlan: {
+  type: String,
+  enum: ['starter', 'bisnis', 'lifetime', null],
+  default: null
+},
+subscriptionHistory: [{
+  plan: String,
+  amount: Number,
+  startDate: Date,
+  endDate: Date,
+  merchantOrderId: String,
+  paidAt: Date
+}],
+gracePeriodEndsAt: {
+  type: Date,
+  default: null
+},
```

- Status `'paid'` → direname `'active'` (lebih jelas semantik)
- Status `'grace'` = masa tenggang 3 hari setelah `subscriptionExpiresAt`
- `subscriptionHistory` = log riwayat pembayaran (audit trail)

