### 4. Backend — Socket.io Tenant Rooms

Ubah Socket.io connection handler agar client join ke room berdasarkan tenant slug.

#### [MODIFY] [server.js](file:///d:/DevAppTim/Warkop%20React%20-%20%20SuperKafe%20Multitenant/backend/server.js)

```diff
 io.on('connection', (socket) => {
   console.log('⚡ Client connected:', socket.id);
+
+  // Join tenant room for targeted events
+  socket.on('join:tenant', (tenantSlug) => {
+    if (tenantSlug) {
+      socket.join(tenantSlug);
+      console.log(`📎 ${socket.id} joined room: ${tenantSlug}`);
+    }
+  });
 
   socket.on('disconnect', () => {
     console.log('🔌 Client disconnected:', socket.id);
   });
 });
```

