## Architecture Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant WebBrowser as 🌐 Web Browser
    participant MobileApp as 📱 Mobile App
    participant Backend as ⚙️ Backend API
    participant Duitku as 💰 Duitku Gateway
    participant SocketIO as 🔌 Socket.io

    Note over WebBrowser: User buka halaman Billing
    WebBrowser->>Backend: POST /payments/create-invoice
    Backend->>Duitku: Create Payment
    Duitku-->>Backend: paymentUrl
    Backend-->>WebBrowser: Redirect ke Duitku
    WebBrowser->>Duitku: User bayar
    Duitku->>Backend: POST /payments/callback
    Backend->>Backend: Update Tenant status → active
    Backend->>SocketIO: emit subscription:updated
    SocketIO->>MobileApp: subscription:updated event
    MobileApp->>MobileApp: Update UI real-time (Lock Screen hilang)

    Note over MobileApp: User buka app
    MobileApp->>Backend: GET /tenants/:slug/trial-status
    Backend-->>MobileApp: {status, plan, expiresAt}
    alt Expired (after grace)
        MobileApp->>MobileApp: Show Lock Screen
    else Grace Period
        MobileApp->>MobileApp: Show Grace Banner
    else Active
        MobileApp->>MobileApp: Show Normal UI
    end
```

